{
  "id": "adv_main_01_06_06",
  "title": "星見編2章1話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_lesson-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-3d",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（サニーピースと月のテンペストが）\n（同時デビューを果たしてから一週間が経った）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It’s been a week since Sunny Peace and Moon Tempest）\n（made their joint debut.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.883161142468453,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（星見市の野外ステージで公演をしたことで、市内では）\n（ そこそこの知名度を獲得することができたが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The outdoor live they put on in Hoshimi）\n（has led to them gaining some recognition within the city.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "1、2、3、4、1、2、3、4……！\n白石さん、出遅れてます！ リズム意識して！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "1‚ 2‚ 3‚ 4‚ 1‚ 2‚ 3‚ 4…\nShiraishi-san‚ you’re falling behind. Keep up with the rhythm!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.23333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい……っ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-sorry…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "兵藤さんは動きが小さ過ぎます！\nもっと手足を大きく広く動かして！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hyodo-san‚ your movements are too small.\nMove your legs and arms more!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.46210882663728,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "なんだかすごいね、怜ちゃん\n私が教わってた先生より怖いかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei-chan is really something else.\nI think she’s more terrifying than my old coach.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.86210882663729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それだけ真剣なんだろう\nダンス大会の優勝経験者だしな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just shows how serious she is about this.\nShe’s won a dance championship‚ after all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.62284850608346,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（デビュー公演で怜は、痛感したんだろう）\n（ 今のサニピの実力ではグランプリを勝ち上がれないと）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（During their debut live‚ it must’ve been painfully evident to Rei）\n（that Sunny Peace wouldn’t be able to win the Grand Prix at their current level.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.0561818394168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "1、2、3、4、1\n……きゃっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "1‚ 2‚ 3‚ 4‚ 1.\nEek!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.84067168818272,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "さ、さくらちゃん\n大丈夫？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Sakura-chan!\nAre you okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.64067168818272,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あはは……大丈夫です\nちょっと足がもつれちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha… Yeah.\nMy feet just got tangled up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.05477423394537,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_dangerous-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 59.82144090061204
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "今のはしっかり足が\n上がってなかったからですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s because you weren’t\nraising legs high enough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.18810756727871,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "うん……ごめん\nもう一回頭からやってみよう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right… My bad.\nLet‘s start over again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.58810756727871,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "待って、少し休憩入れよっか\nさくらちゃん、マッサージしてあげるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hold on. Let’s take a short break.\nSakura-chan‚ I’ll give your legs massage",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.6881075672787,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "休憩って……\nまだ始めて一時間も経ってませんよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A break?\nIt’s been less than an hour since we started.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.82144090061205,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "でも……怜ちゃんや、一応アイドルとして先輩の私は\n踊り慣れてるから平気だけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Rei-chan… you and I have dance experience‚\nso it’s easy for us to keep up like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.65477423394539,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "だからこそ、みんなのペースに\n合わせた方がいいと思うの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why I think we should be\nmatching everyone else’s pace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.12144090061206,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "合わせるって……\nそれ、練習のレベルを下げるってことですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Match their pace?\nDoesn’t that mean lowering the level of practice?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.7418112250648,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "…………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.50847789173146,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いったん休憩しよう。高みを目指す怜の考えも分かる\nでも、無理して体を壊しちゃ元も子もないだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s break for now. I understand Rei’s desire to aim high‚\nbut there’s no point in overdoing it and injuring yourselves.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.44181122506478,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "…………え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "………Eh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.66409071151364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "確かにそうなんだけど……\nそれ{user}君が言っても……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You have a point‚ but…\nThat’s not very convincing coming from you‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.91409073788876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "この前、過労で倒れたのって誰でしたっけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who was it that collapsed from overworking the other day?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.83409073615024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "う……説得力ないか。迷惑かけたしな\nほんと、すみません……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right… I deserve that after what I put you all through.\nI’m really sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.11513374113986,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、みんなまだ体力もついてないですし\n休憩しないとキツそうですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it’s true that not all of us have built up enough stamina yet‚\nso it might be tough without breaks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.88180040780657,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "けど、ダラダラ休んでも意味ないですから……\n休憩はきっかり十分にしましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Still‚ there’s no point in lazing around.\nWe’ll keep our break to precisely 10 minutes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.18180040780663,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（怜をグループに入れた効果は出ているな）\n（ けど問題は別の場所にもあるか）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The effects of having Rei in the group are really showing.）\n（But there are other problems as well.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.48180040780647,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8418.19959219353,
          "startTime": 151.9
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-fs-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3166.6666666665433,
          "startTime": 146.64846707447302
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ん？ 電話か……三枝さんから？\n……お疲れ様です。どうしました？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ I’m getting a call… Saegusa-san?\nHello‚ is everything alright?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.04846707447325,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 156.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shj.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06-shj001.m4a",
      "text": "グランプリについてだ。すぐに発表されるだろうが……\n今回のグランプリ、予選が組まれるそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s about the Grand Prix. This should be announced soon‚\nbut it looks like they’ll be setting up preliminary rounds.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.91513374113995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shj.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_06-shj002.m4a",
